OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778181071
OL,3,CFootball club 'extremely disappointed'
OL,4,Cas play-off final venue switched
OL,6,FGuernsey FC say they are "extremely
OL,7,Fdisappointed and frustrated" after
OL,8,Fleague officials decided to switch the
OL,9,Fvenue for their play-off final match
OL,10,Fagainst Peacehaven and Telescombe.
OL,12,FThe club expected to play the crucial
OL,13,FSouthern Combination Football League
OL,14,F(SCFL) promotion decider at Victoria
OL,15,FPark in St Sampsons on Sunday 10 May,
OL,16,Fbut now face a trip to the UK instead.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
