FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778181071
OL,3,CFootball club 'extremely disappointed'
OL,4,Cas play-off final venue switched
OL,6,FIt may be played on the following
OL,7,FTuesday or Wednesday, with details
OL,8,Fstill to be confirmed, while the Green
OL,9,FLions are considering a formal appeal
OL,10,Fto the FA.
OL,12,FIn a statement, the club explain: "The
OL,13,Fright to home advantage was earned on
OL,14,Fmerit through a third-place league
OL,15,Ffinish and victory in our semi-final.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778181071
OL,3,CFootball club 'extremely disappointed'
OL,4,Cas play-off final venue switched
OL,6,F"The removal of the opportunity to
OL,7,Fhost what would have been a major
OL,8,Foccasion, in front of a large crowd,
OL,9,Fundermines the integrity of the
OL,10,Fcompetition and is a position the club
OL,11,Fdoes not accept."
OL,13,FGuernsey FC add that many supporters
OL,14,Ffrom both sides have already booked
OL,15,Ftravel and accommodation "in good
OL,16,Ffaith", preparing for the originally
OL,17,Fscheduled match.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778181071
OL,3,CFootball club 'extremely disappointed'
OL,4,Cas play-off final venue switched
OL,6,FThe club say they are "deeply
OL,7,Fconcerned" that this does not appear
OL,8,Fto have been taken into account,
OL,9,Fstating they first received
OL,10,Fconfirmation of the change at around
OL,11,F5:30pm on Monday 4 May.
OL,13,FThey explain: "The league has cited
OL,14,Fcomplex travel arrangements as
OL,15,Fjustification. However, this position
OL,16,Fwas reached without affording the club
OL,17,Fthe opportunity to address or mitigate
OL,18,Fthose concerns.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778181071
OL,3,CFootball club 'extremely disappointed'
OL,4,Cas play-off final venue switched
OL,6,F"Given the limited timeframe since the
OL,7,Fvenue was confirmed on Saturday, and
OL,8,Fthe inability to progress discussions
OL,9,Fover the Bank Holiday, the club
OL,10,Fconsiders this outcome to be premature
OL,11,Fand disproportionate.
OL,13,F"This morning (Wednesday 6 May), we
OL,14,Fwere informed that our proposed travel
OL,15,Farrangements had been considered by
OL,16,FPeacehaven and Telescombe, who were
OL,17,Funable to agree to the proposal on a
OL,18,Fnumber of grounds.
OL,26,@uD@OpmuD@_pn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778181071
OL,3,CFootball club 'extremely disappointed'
OL,4,Cas play-off final venue switched
OL,6,F"This raises further concern that
OL,7,FPeacehaven have effectively been given
OL,8,Fdiscretion over whether the fixture is
OL,9,Fplayed in Guernsey, rather than the
OL,10,Fleague enforcing the fixture at the
OL,11,Fvenue earned on sporting merit and
OL,12,Funder the competition regulations."
OL,14,FDespite the Green Lions saying that
OL,15,Fthe league has made a final decision,
OL,16,Fthey stress: "We will continue to
OL,17,Fpursue all appropriate avenues to
OL,18,Fsecure a fair and proper outcome for
OL,19,Fplayers, supporters and all parties
OL,20,Finvolved.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1778181071
OL,3,CFootball club 'extremely disappointed'
OL,4,Cas play-off final venue switched
OL,6,F"We remain hopeful that, alongside the
OL,7,FSCFL and Peacehaven and Telescombe, a
OL,8,Fsensible and fair solution can still
OL,9,Fbe found."
OL,11,FITV News put these concerns to the
OL,12,FSCFL, which declined to comment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
